        <div class="glass-card-service p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Zero to MVP in 14 Days
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Skip the endless planning. Get a battle-tested product in your
            users' hands in two weeks flat. Built to scale, ready to dominate.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card-service p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            AI That Means Business
          </h3>
